-- Chelsea to Play Paris Saint-Germain in Yankee Stadium Exhibition
-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 2012-05-07T14:57:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-07/chelsea-to-play-paris-saint-germain-in-yankee-stadium-exhibition.html
Chelsea will play Paris Saint-Germain
at Yankee Stadium in New York in an exhibition soccer match on
July 22.  It will be the first soccer match at the stadium, which
opened in 2009.  Chelsea, of London, last week reached the  Champions League 
final with a victory over Barcelona. PSG leads the French
League.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  